<p class="">It would be better for us to wait and see the Bill, but I must say that there is a great deal in the statement of the right hon. Gentleman which seems to show that the rights and feelings of the House will have full opportunity of expression when the time comes.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
